Method.СообщитьПользователю.Example.Description=1. To Output Setting U Fields upravlyaemoy Form, svyazannogo C rekvizitom Form\:\nObshchegoNaznacheniyaKlientServer.MessageToUser(\nNStr("ru \= 'Message On O.'"), ,\n"PoleVRekviziteFormyObekt",\n"Object");\nAlternativnyy Settings Composition In Form Form\:\nObshchegoNaznacheniyaKlientServer.MessageToUser(\nNStr("ru \= 'Message On O.'"), ,\n"Object.PoleVRekviziteFormyObekt");\n2. To Output Setting Next C polem upravlyaemoy Form, svyazannym C rekvizitom Form\:\nObshchegoNaznacheniyaKlientServer.MessageToUser(\nNStr("ru \= 'Message On O.'"), ,\n"ImyaRekvizitaFormy");\n3. To Output Setting svyazannogo C obektom Directory Base\:\nObshchegoNaznacheniyaKlientServer.MessageToUser(\nNStr("ru \= 'Message On O.'"), ObektInformatsionnoyBazy, "Otvetstvennyy",,Otkaz);\n4. To Output Setting By Ref To Object Directory Base\:\nObshchegoNaznacheniyaKlientServer.MessageToUser(\nNStr("ru \= 'Message On O.'"), Ref, , , Otkaz);\nSluchai nekorrektnogo Composition\:\n1. Data odnovremenno Table KlyuchDannykh T PutKDannym.\n2. Data In parametre KlyuchDannykh Form Type otlichnogo From dopustimykh.\n3. Setting References Debug Rights Fields (T/Or puti S Data).\n@Skip-Check Method-too-many-Params
